query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('android',
'money',
'security',
'sharepoint',
'travel')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('2013',
'canada',
'credit-card',
'customs-and-immigration',
'document-library',
'investing',
'malware',
'search',
'sharepoint-online',
'stocks',
'tls',
'transit',
'united-states',
'web-part',
'workflow')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
